
1. Disable PHP Error Reporting
Paste into the wp-config.php file.
  
error_reporting(0);
@ini_set(‘display_errors’, 0);

2. Turn Off File Editing
Paste into the wp-config.php file.
  
define( ‘DISALLOW_FILE_EDIT’, true );

3. Protect the wp-config.php File
Paste into the .htaccess file.

<files wp-config.php>
order allow,deny
deny from all
</files>

 Make sure to back up your website before working 
